lead_paragraph: Decisions by the coaches of the Lions and Wellington Hurricanes to take a gamble in the last round of Super Rugby's regular season may have influenced the outcome of the competition's final on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Last-Round Gambles Had Bearing on Super Final Outcome
